OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA damp morning in the east with
OL,6,Frain clearing. Sunny spells through
OL,7,Fthe afternoon with cloud thickening
OL,8,Ffrom the west later with freshening
OL,9,Fwinds. Feeling less mild.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FCloudier this evening with a
OL,12,Ffew showers in the west. Turning wet
OL,13,Fand windy during the early hours with
OL,14,Fpersistent rain by dawn. Generally
OL,15,Ffeeling a little milder.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSunday:FAn unsettled start with
OL,18,Foutbreaks of rain, heaviest and most
OL,19,Fpersistent over the hills. Somewhat
OL,20,Fdrier into the afternoon through still
OL,21,Fdrizzle in places. Windy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
