OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,6,FFurther spells of rain on Monday with
OL,7,Flighter winds. Drier overall on
OL,8,FTuesday and Wednesday with higher
OL,9,Fpressure in charge. Staying mild with
OL,10,Fwinds easing.
